ing: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">是否按照要求进行公示</span></p></td><td width=\"433\" valign=\"center\" style=\"padding: 0px;border-width: 1px;border-color: windowtext\"><p style=\"text-align: center; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">是</span></span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"><td width=\"177\" valign=\"center\" style=\"padding: 0px;border-width: 1px;border-color: windowtext\"><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">公示网站名称及网址（以其他形式进行</span></p><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">公示的也需列明）</span></p></td><td width=\"433\" valign=\"center\" style=\"padding: 0px;border-width: 1px;border-color: windowtext\"><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">南昌为力人力资源服务有限公司</span></p><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">www.jxwlrl.com</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"><td width=\"177\" valign=\"center\" style=\"padding: 0px;border-width: 1px;border-color: windowtext\"><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">开始公示时间</span></p></td><td width=\"433\" valign=\"center\" style=\"padding: 0px;border-width: 1px;border-color: windowtext\"><p style=\";border: 0px;line-height: 30px;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 19px\">2020年5月11号</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"><td width=\"177\" valign=\"center\"